ke\" data-send=\"false\" data-href=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/rhubarb-sauce/\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"105\" data-show-faces=\"false\" data-action=\"like\"></div>\n<div class=\"pinterest\">\n<a href=\"http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com%2Frecipes%2Frhubarb-sauce%2F&media=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com/recipes/rhubarb-sauce/rhubarb-sauce_large.jpg&description=Simple%20Rhubarb%20Sauce\" class=\"pin-it-button\" count-layout=\"horizontal\">Pin It</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"print\"><a href=\"/pdfs/rhubarb-sauce.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Simple Rhubarb Sauce');\"><img src=\"/img/icons/print.png\" alt=\"Print\" /></a><a href=\"/pdfs/rhubarb-sauce.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Simple Rhubarb Sauce');\">Print or download (PDF)</a></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\">\n<li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/\">Recipes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/desserts/\"><span itemprop=\"recipeCategory\">Desserts</span></a></li>\n<li>Simple Rhubarb Sauce</li>\n</ul>\n<div itemprop=\"description\" class=\"description\">A tangy sauce that makes a wonderful springtime dessert or snack.</div>\n<div class=\"stats\">\n<ul>\n<li>Prep: <meta itemprop=\"prepTime\" value=\"PT10M\"/>10 min</li>\n<li>Rise: <meta itemprop=\"riseTime\" value=\"PT1H\"/>1 hour</li>\n<li>Cook: <meta itemprop=\"cookTime\" value=\"PT15M\"/>15 min</li>\n<li>Total: <meta itemprop=\"totalTime\" value=\"PT1H25M\"/>1 hour 25 min</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeYield\">Serves 4 to 6</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"steps\">\n<div class=\"right\">\n<a href=\"/recipes/rhubarb-sauce/rhubarb-sauce_large.jpg\"><img class=\"polaroid\" src=\"/recipes/rhubarb-sauce/rhubarb-sauce.jpg\" alt=\"Simple Rhubarb Sauce\" itemprop=\"image\"/></a>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">8 stalks of rhubarb</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Cut off the ends of the rhubarb and rinse well. Chop rhubarb into 1 inch pieces.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac14; cup of water</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Place rhubarb pieces in a large saucepan and add water. Cover and cook over high heat until soft, about 10 minutes.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 &frac12; - 2 cups of sugar, to taste</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Reduce heat to medium high and add sugar, &frac12; cup at a time stirring to incorporate completely. Taste periodically and add sugar as desired. Total sugar required depends both on your taste and on the tartness of the rhubarb.</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Remove from heat and pour into a glass bowl or other container. Cover with plastic wrap and chill for at least one hour before serving. Keeps for up to a week in the refrigerator.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"footnote\">\n<div class=\"logo\">MakeBetterFood.com</div>\nFrom MakeBetterFood.com. <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2012-04-18\">Apr 18, 2012</time>. (http://makebetterfood.com/recipes/rhubarb-sauce/). Adapted from the kitchen of Catharine Ahalt.\n</div>\n<!-- Microformat Ingredients -->\n<ul class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">8 stalks of rhubarb</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac14; cup of water</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 &frac12; - 2 cups of sugar, to taste</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Microformat Steps -->\n<ol class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Cut off the ends of the rhubarb and rinse well. Chop rhubarb into 1 inch pieces.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Place rhubarb pieces in a large saucepan and add water. Cover and cook over high heat until soft, about 10 minutes.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Reduce heat to medium high and add sugar, &frac12; cup at a time stirring to incorporate completely. Taste periodically and add sugar as desired. Total sugar required depends both on your taste and on the tartness of the rhubarb.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Remove from heat and pour into a glass bowl or other container. Cover with plastic wrap and chill for at least one hour before serving. Keeps for up to a week in the refrigerator.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<h4>Related Equipment or Ingredients</h4>\n<div class=\"pushTop10 clearfix polarioidSummaryRow\">\n<div class=\"polaroidSummary\">\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/All-Clad-5204-Stainless-4-Quart-Saucepan/dp/B00005AL5N?SubscriptionId=AKIAJT76QZNN5CAIGPSQ&tag=makbetfoo-20&linkCode=xm2&camp=2025&creative=165953&creativeASIN=B00005AL5N\"><img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41SAKTTHMKL.SL100_AA105.jpg\" alt=\"All-Clad Stainless 4-Quart Saucepan\" class=\"\"/>\nAll-Clad Stainless 4-Quart Saucepan</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<div class=\"grid_2 alpha\">\n<img src=\"/img/cookbook/cover_bestof_grid3.png\" alt=\"Best of Make Better Food\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 138px; width:100%;\" class=\"dropShadow\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid_10 omega\">\n<h4>Get New Recipes via Email + Free Cookbook</h4>\n<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n<form action=\"http://makebetterfood.us5.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=23bb9cd41955f33d8db8c9e91&amp;id=f2cac69129\" method=\"post\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" name=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" class=\"validate clear pushTop10\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-error-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-success-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<input type=\"email\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"email\" name=\"EMAIL\" class=\"xlarge\" id=\"mce-EMAIL\" size=\"30\" onclick=\"clearEmail(this);\" onfocus=\"clearEmail(this);\" onblur=\"fillEmail(this);\" style=\"color: #222;\" required=\"required\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" class=\"btn primary\" name=\"subscribe\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe\" value=\"Subscribe and Get Your Free Cookbook\">\n</form>\n<!--End mc_embed_signup-->\n<p